  <h3>Collaboration</h3>
  <p>WWe love teaming up with people on projects of all shapes and sizes…</p>
  <ul>
    <li>with for people who have great ideas for a project, product or business they are starting, but don’t have the technical know-how to get there.</li>
    <li>with other talented developers who need a bit of extra help to polish up a few details on a project, whether it is lending an extra hand, or to bring our specific expertise to fill in gaps in knowledge.</li>
